---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

const demoUrl = 'https://demo.poesis.cloud';
---
<BaseLayout title="Poesis">
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="motto">Define the world in software; generate it in software.</p>
      <h1>Harnessing the generative AI era so that systems continuously develop on their own.</h1>
      <p class="lead">Today, IT's Think — governance and specifications — live in prose — architecture wiki, compliance spreadsheets, review boards — that drifts from reality the moment it is written. Poesis stack turns that prose into governed, typed, versioned, <strong>machine-operable</strong> <i>definitions</i> it can act on, generate from, and continuously enforce.</p>
      <div class="hero-cta">
        <a class="btn btn-primary" href={demoUrl}>Try now</a>
        <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="#portfolio">Explore the portfolio</a>
        <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="/contact">Talk to us</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="portfolio" class="section section--soft">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-head">
        <p class="eyebrow">Portfolio</p>
        <h2>An open standard, the engine, the application — and the agentic AI that generate.</h2>
        <p class="lead">GSM roots the <i>definitions</i> into systemics field; SIE operates the <i>definitions</i>; ITIP applies SIE to IT; the SAFe Agentic generates <i>definitions</i> and operational artifacts from <i>definitions</i>; and Poesis services deliver the change. Each piece links to the other to close the IT Think-Build-Run loop, <string>systematically and autonomously</strong>, <string>with human in the loop.</strong></p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid grid-2" style="margin-top:1.5rem">
        <div class="card">
          <span class="tag tag--muted">Application</span>
          <h3>ITIP</h3>
          <p>The IT Intelligence Platform — the first domain application, built on SIE, that governs the IT landscape as a single source of truth.</p>
          <p style="margin-top:.6rem"><a href="/itip">About ITIP →</a></p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <span class="tag tag--muted">Engine</span>
          <h3>SIE</h3>
          <p>The Systemic Intelligence Engine — the engine that implements GSM and operates definitions, enforcing their lifecycle, and powers every domain application above it.</p>
          <p style="margin-top:.6rem"><a href="/sie">About SIE →</a></p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <span class="tag">Standard</span>
          <h3>GSM</h3>
          <p>The Generative System Model — the open, vendor-neutral standard for defining and governing systems. Free, open, the top of every funnel.</p>
          <p style="margin-top:.6rem"><a href="/standard">About GSM →</a></p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <span class="tag tag--muted">Framework + Portfolio</span>
          <h3>SAFe Agentic</h3>
          <p>The open (Apache-2.0) BUILD layer — a portfolio-to-iteration orchestration of AI agents that turns governed definitions into Build artifacts, an analytical, auditable, and reviewable way.</p>
          <p style="margin-top:.6rem"><a href="/framework">About SAFe Agentic →</a></p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <span class="tag tag--muted">Services</span>
          <h3>Transformation</h3>
          <p>AI-generative, agentic transformation of your organization — IT first — delivered with the Poesis stack as the governed substrate.</p>
          <p style="margin-top:.6rem"><a href="/services">How we engage →</a></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section--ink">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="eyebrow">Our first custody</p>
      <h2>Poesis runs on Poesis.</h2>
      <p class="lead">We are our own first customer. The Poesis stack that will integrate your systems already define, build, and govern ours — Poesis's development power rests on the very stack it ships.</p>
      <div class="hero-cta">
        <a class="btn btn-primary" href={demoUrl}>Try the ITIP demo</a>
        <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="https://github.com/poesis-cloud" style="background:transparent;color:#fff;border-color:#334155">See it on GitHub</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
